data.description: Discover your cozy mountain retreat in Colfax - a delightful A-frame home nestled among majestic pines. This charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom property features a well-appointed main level, while a spacious loft invites creative possibilities. The  modern kitchen, adorned with granite counters and equipped with updated appliances, complements the airy feel. Sunlight dances through expansive windows, illuminating the vaulted living room adorned with a wood-burning stove. An attached  2-car garage with workshop/laundry area, plus a detached carport, offers ample space. Embrace outdoor living on the rear deck or covered breezeway, perfect for BBQs and gatherings.  With a metal roof, dual pane windows, and a cleared landscape, this haven is ready for you. Just 10-12 minutes from Rollins Lake and I-80, 15 minutes to town, and approximately 45 minutes to ski resorts, your serene mountain lifestyle awaits.
